<A>__{joan, her mood light hearted, enters, with duke following. she crosses to the closet, selects a change of clothes and moves to lay them out on the bed. noting the message light blinking on her answering machine, she steps over to the night stand, presses the playback and to a series of tones preceding the recorded messages,}
<B>__{moves out of frame.}
<L>__{interior andy's house bathroom night}
<A>__{the indistinct sounds of a taped message over: joan turns the tap on in the wash basin and begins splashing water on her face. then as she reaches to a towel and turns the tap off, the words of a popular rock song can be heard. exhibiting some curiosity, she exits the bathroom.}
